The other thing about validate_doc_update is that ordering isn't important. Any function can veto the update. But for mutation operations if we allow any number of functions then your function has to accept any possible configuration of the order of applying those functions. And it has to work with possibly unknown other code in the same db. Basically the possibilities started hurting my brain so I just went with the url approach.<br/>

