item.description:
When requesting a document from CouchDB it is served by &quot;CouchDB/0.9.0 (Erlang OTP/R12B)&quot; according to the Server header, but when requesting a document through a show function seems to be served by &quot;MochiWeb/1.0 (Any of you quaids got a smint?)&quot;.<br/>
